5:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-blue-50 py-14","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-anton text-3xl uppercase mb-6 text-text-main text-center","children":["Local Roads and Driving Conditions in ","Sherwood"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 mb-10 text-center mx-auto","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"Looking for driving lessons in Sherwood? UNO Driving School provides calm, automatic driving lessons for learners across Sherwood, Graceville, Corinda and Oxley. Our 5-star instructors help Sherwood students pass their Queensland driving test confidently on the first attempt."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"Sherwood is one of Brisbane's most charming riverside western suburbs, and its road environment is both varied and highly suitable for learner training. Sherwood Road is the main arterial — moderately busy, well-maintained and featuring the Sherwood State School zone and several important intersections. The quieter riverside streets near Sherwood Forest Park provide a calm starting environment for beginner lessons."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"The Sherwood Arboretum and the surrounding parkland streets create a genuinely pleasant driving environment that our instructors use deliberately for early lesson sequencing. Starting a lesson near leafy, lower-traffic streets before progressing to the broader Sherwood Road corridor is exactly the kind of structured approach that builds lasting driver confidence."}],["$","p","3",{"children":"Sherwood learners test at the Woolloongabba Transport and Main Roads Centre. Free pickup from Sherwood, Afterpay on all packages. Book your Sherwood lesson today."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-blue-100 flex items-start gap-4","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-primary text-xl mt-0.5